  "decomposition_rationale": "The OrderSystem is decomposed into three main workflows (PlaceOrder, CancelOrder, TrackOrder) based on the command, each with its own sub-steps. ParseAndValidateInput handles input validation for all commands. PlaceOrder further decomposes into ValidateItemsAndStock, ChargePayment, ReserveInventory, and CreateOrderRecord to ensure atomicity. CancelOrder decomposes into VerifyOrderNotShipped, RefundPayment, RestoreInventory, and UpdateOrderStatus. TrackOrder is a simple query. All children are self-contained and do not call siblings; the parent orchestrates based on command.",
